data.description: Nestled in the heart of St. Clair Shores, this inviting 3-bedroom, 1-bath ranch presents a remarkable opportunity for those seeking a residence ready for personalized touches. Boasting spacious bedrooms tailored to accommodate each family member comfortably, this home beckons with the promise of creating cherished memories. Additionally, the property's strategic location in St. Clair Shores adds another layer of appeal, placing it in proximity to a variety of amenities that cater to your individual needs. Whether it's the nearby parks, schools, or shopping centers, this residence seamlessly integrates convenience into daily life. With the promise of a residence primed for personalization and a location that caters to diverse lifestyle preferences, seize the opportunity to schedule your showing without delay. Your journey toward a tailor-made home experience begins now.
